<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Matematika 1 - Buy</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* Reset some default styles */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--background-color);
            color: var(--text-color);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            width: 500px;
            text-align: center;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

        h1 {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: var(--text-color);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .buy-button {
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 300px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .buy-button:hover {
            background-color: var(--secondary-color);
        }

        /* Colors using CSS Variables */
        :root {
            --primary-color: #2563eb;
            --secondary-color: #1d4ed8;
            --background-color: #f8fafc;
            --text-color: #1e293b;
        }

        /* Responsive adjustments */
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                padding: 20px;
                width: 90%;
            }
            h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>Matematika - Prvi Kolokvij</h1>
        <p>
            This is the first exam of the "Matematika 1" course. It’s designed to help you assess your understanding 
            of key mathematical concepts. Don’t miss your chance to secure your place!
        </p>
        <p><strong>Price:</strong> €30.00</p>
        <form action="/checkout1" method="post">
            <input type="submit" class="buy-button" value="Proceed to Buy">
        </form>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
